EPILOGUE:

 

This gangster was bitter....before

 

This gangster doesn't believe in the existence of love....before

 

This gangster was hurt twice

 

 

But this bitter gangster... fell inlove...again.

 

 


But this time, she was not hurt.

 

 

 

 

She will be loved forever, even in heaven.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 


R.I.P

Vianne Michelle Valderama

October 6,1996- June, 21 2012

 

 

 

''Grabe, kahit hindi sila nagpakasal. Kitang kita mo na, mahal nila ang isa't isa, sinakripisyo nila ang buhay nila para sa isa't isa.'' Sabi ni Bree.

 

 

''You're right bree. Your ate via, is happy with him.'' 

 

 

''Mommy. I'll miss kuya.'' Nilagay ni Bree ang flowers sa puntod ng kuya niya.

 

 

 

 

R.I.P

 

Xian Patrick Reyes

February 24,1996- June 21,2012

 

 


''Dont cry baby..'' Niyakap lang siya ng nanay niya.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

.....

 

 

''I love you bebi.'' Sabi ko kay Xian. Habang tinitignan yung mga ibon na lumilipad. Tapos yung asul na asul na kulay ng dagat.

 

 

''I love you too bebi. Forever... kahit dito pa sa heaven. Walang hanggan.'' Hinalikan niya ako sa labi.

 

 

We are married.

 

Heaven is our church

Angels are the audience 

God is the priest.

 

 

 

In the story endings, earth will be the place to forever

But for our story, my story

 

 

 


Heaven is the place for my happy ending.

 

-END

 

